          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — full local SEO cycle: claim, audit, citations, GBP posts, rank tracking.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — time saved per week, rank movement, NAP accuracy, cost.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $1,920 across 10 tools, Apr–Jun 2026.</li>
        </ul>

